        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6467",
        "content": "\"Oh, I'm going in for study this session,\" answered Tom demurely. And then he winked at Larry on the sly.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
